Utilizes a dateStringEditor custom directive for the month/day/year portion of the datetime, providing a text box with a date-picker button ({@link https://angular-ui.github.io/bootstrap/#/datepicker|ui-bootstrap})

Utilizes a timeStringEditor custom directive for the hour/minute/second portion of the datetime, providing a textbox with a "time-picker" dropdown

@param {string} [dateFormat] - format string for date portion {@link https://docs.angularjs.org/api/ng/filter/date} 
  if not present, defaults to "MMMM dd, yyyy"
@param {string} [timeFormat] - format string for time portion
  if not present, defaults to "h:mm a"
